comment: Batum (POR) and Lee (MEM) briefly engage as Batum cuts away from the ball.
Batum (POR) takes two steps after catching the pass. Players are allowed to use their two steps to go in any direction.
Lopez (POR) makes contact with Randolph's (MEM) arm and the contact affects his movement to the basket and shot attempt.
Aldridge (POR) sets the screen on Allen (MEM) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Allen (MEM).
Batum (POR) commits a take foul on Gasol (MEM) after the ball has been inbounded.
Allen (MEM) makes contact with Lillard (POR) that causes him to lose control of the ball on the drive to the basket.
Prior to the inbounds, Batum (POR) has two hands on Gasol's (MEM) waist and his FOM is restricted as he attempts to get open.
Batum (POR) makes body contact with Gasol (MEM) that forces him OOB.
Allen (MEM) is in legal guarding position and does not affect Lillard's (POR) RSBQ on the drive to the basket.
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Calathes (MEM).
McCollum (POR) commits a take foul on Green (MEM).
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
Lee (MEM) is not in legal guarding position at the time of the contact with McCollum (POR) on the successful field goal attempt.
Aldridge (POR) commits a take foul on Gasol (MEM).
Randolph (MEM) legally contests Batum's (POR) jump shot and the incidental contact after the release occurs because Batum jumps forward into Randolph.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
Allen (MEM) makes contact with McCollum (POR), but it does not affect his ability to defend the inbounds pass.
Afflalo (POR) commits a take foul on Lee (MEM).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that McCollum (POR) released the shot prior to the game clock expiring was upheld.
